1aTeFTM1TQFYZVXJKJ_!!720462376.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.alicdn.com%2Fi2%2F720462376%2FO1CN01aTeFTM1TQFYZVXJKJ_%21%21720462376.jpg&h=e5626c36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n膨脹PU膠描述 :<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">TYL-泡沫S被修改單組分聚氨酯泡沫填充或接縫和間隙密封</span>。泡沫噴出後迅速膨脹並迅速與空氣中的水分反應固化成精細的蜂窩結構泡沫。它<span style=\"color: red;\">形成了一個強有力的鍵合最建築材料</span>，如混凝土表面上。 TYL-泡沫S被在噴嘴增壓級氣霧罐供應。<br />\n <br />\n膨脹PU膠用途 :<br />\n‧腔填充 <br />\n‧在車頂結構的所有開口密封 <br />\n‧聲學障板的應用 <br />\n‧吸音層的應用 <br />\n‧安裝窗戶和門框 <br />\n <br />\n膨脹PU膠優點 :<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">‧高灌裝能力 </span><br />\n‧高絕緣值，熱學和聲學 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">‧很好的粘結性能 <br />\n‧卓越的穩定性不收縮或膨脹後 </span><br />\n‧無氟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>復活彩蛋</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/bZyV8M4.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"4902c47a15187a66711a01784232829e95209f4c","tid":1650012,"uid":96169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e574617dccc1dd46b2b38bd8d3fe90b03e04b0d3","tid":1650012,"uid":134912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:35:33.000Z","msg":"識唔識冷處理啊 洗唔洗成個熱門都係？<br />\n5個月啦都 過份反應仲唔識改？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:40:34.000Z","msg":"唔可以冷處理今次<br />\n要熱處理<br />\n瘋狂留言其他po <br />\n推上熱門"},{"pid":"e310d2ee4b76f358504009b502be9c805e5b3974","tid":1650012,"uid":312412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:40:40.000Z","msg":"［警告］唔好再比人分化！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1650021\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1650021</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c2994e828e1db1b9fb79be31f97c9db828734b26","tid":1650012,"uid":96169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e79613e80e6dc0616e14b083c1a979a09dad248","tid":1650012,"uid":134912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:38:00.000Z","msg":"唔理係唔係五毛 <br />\n人地就睇中你小事化大 搞你一波 <br />\